{"tid":1362720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試着說反黑大遊行，不要說光復元朗","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:10:21.000Z","uid":268292,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1436a4e4d47ee0c443acd5a36f8345d414e826b3","tid":1362720,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"好明顯721元朗恐襲之後，引起沉默大多數的反應，由總商會到公務員，紛紛出黎表態，將鄉黑問題浮面，更加激發外國對香港發出旅遊警示，呢d應該係政府預料唔到。<br />\n<br />\n星期六本身人數會比星期日少，加上我地打住光復元朗名號更加好令女士，稍為上年紀或者有另一半一齊去嘅人有所考慮，人數會再少d<br />\n<br />\n如果我地今次地區遊行嘅名目係反黑，反警黑合作；不主動入村挑釁，遊行完去元朗西鐵站示威（其實即係南邊圍村口），亦唔建議返去元朗警處示威，因為個邊離最近嘅朗屏站都有一段距離，好難走。<br />\n咁做嘅話，<br />\n1. 可以更聚焦落警黑呢件事<br />\n2. 外國傳媒更加可以煲大件事黎講<br />\n3. 班牛屎佬出師無名<br />\n4. 可以借機拉攏鄉議局派打擊西環插落黎新界嘅勢力（即係中共常用嘅統戰）<br />\n5. 食住而家社會大割席，用鄉黑問題做前鋒帶出我地5大訴求，將佢地捆綁式提出<br />\n<br />\n香港加油<br />\n利申：由舊登到近期都係cd-rom，最近都忍唔住要開ac嘅P牌仔，歡迎起底"},{"pid":"6f7de96f85e9714e7979031ebfcf83123dfb9ef1","tid":1362720,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"304ea62bff8b654bd38e41108c5805344b3f5d4b","tid":1362720,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"54764254011e03ec4827d95598236e43e0475be6","tid":1362720,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"355186765462bb0209183d87085bea234b6163d3","tid":1362720,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFqibUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFqibUD.jpg&h=ebc0d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRtS0NX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRtS0NX.jpg&h=7578d7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗最大連儂牆準備上線啦"},{"pid":"3c6a34017c1b680f747618770518fcf51ad2eb8f","tid":1362720,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bd2ca0c1ba647802da01f8ffad6c29e4b5483c0","tid":1362720,"uid":268292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:27:16.000Z","msg":"同埋入黑一定要撤退，係人地地頭硬碰無着數"},{"pid":"7f9c7c5b2eb49c022541883db6201d8c693a9cec","tid":1362720,"uid":287173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反恐大遊行</span></span> 唔該"},{"pid":"0add81140f07ff9bbf4323e68eb1b5bc48db6e44","tid":1362720,"uid":24734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味成個熱門都係一堆垃圾po<br />\n正正經經起個題冇人理 咪撚連登content farm化<br />\n唔好乜鳩都突發 做好分類得唔撚得呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[策略討論]唔想有用po沉底 就應該統一標題關鍵字嚟分類</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361773</a>"},{"pid":"dd2a35da984ab23ce8d40148a6096b00af1f6d72","tid":1362720,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:45:16.000Z","msg":"【毋忘上環】7.28上環追究開槍大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［更新］726 727 728 84 行動整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358126</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n葵芳宜家有公民廣場，要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360493</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[更正] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n727元朗，對家已開始發放假消息洗鄉民腦[附對策]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"2ec4edcbbf63aa82e3ab72562703e4520a00fca8","tid":1362720,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要，幫手推下同正評得唔得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 打完飛機未，打完就入黎傾正經野呀！！ 727 反黑遊行 5+1 訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpKauS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpKauS</a><br />\n<br />\n順便幫你推埋"},{"pid":"c5575d29312cc64ab256ccb66d0aa11b75b40216","tid":1362720,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><code>（瞄準政權）上環黑警36槍企圖殺害抗爭者 中共策劃元朗恐襲</code></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">所有嘢都係中共係背後策劃<br />\n如果呢個政權係仆街係十惡不赦<br />\n咁擁護佢嘅黑警 黑社會都一樣咁仆街<br />\n咁十惡不赦 但唔好浪費咁多時間係呢<br />\n班卒仔到 <br />\n主力打大佬 瞄準返中共 唔好out focus唔係就真係對唔住咁多位被呢個政權殺害嘅戰友</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LYjFvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LYjFvR.jpg&h=d444c005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">義士宣言：不排除成立臨時立法會</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721宣言</span></span>  <br />\n    <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=fc5995f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350879</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">[長文] 時代周刊直指港府失去管治香港能力嘅分析</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356861</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持前線所有決定</strong></span></div></span><br />\n民情，輿論，選票，呢啲唔洗我哋去諗，點去收拾所謂嘅殘局，就交比啲政治人物去煩啦<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要做嘅係我哋認為啱嘅事</span></strong></div><br />\n<code>「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）</code><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求，勿忘初衷\n遍地開花，不撤不散\n打倒軍權，反對國家恐怖主義\n光復香港，時代革命</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察戰線:</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gq6kYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gq6kYx.jpg&h=1f5648e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hY7P3bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhY7P3bT.jpg&h=5c1777d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定性721黑警上環血腥鎮壓，元朗黑社會恐怖襲擊，警黑合作散播中國國家恐怖主義:<br />\n警察冇預警下開槍射36發橡膠彈，有人爆頭，警察已無視通例，已失去合法性<br />\n警察放任黑社會打市民，完全冇制止，並假指無發現武器收隊，傳媒發現雙方實有公開溝通<br />\n警察公然無視電話求助，元朗警署落閘，違反警隊職責<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會戰線:</span></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7DWJcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7DWJcw.jpg&h=92c6a934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idEKR5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidEKR5S.jpg&h=e6380dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉攏任何政治冷感市民，有錢人，元朗問題非個別事件，收錢恐襲任何區都會發生，任何人都有機會中招<br />\n俾藍絲睇到佢地支持何君堯即係支持黑社會打人斬人，令藍絲同何君堯反面<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際戰線:</span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒巴團隊</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/RhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FRhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay%2Fgiphy.gif&h=254e8117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLink:<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=da2fc471\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/</a><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=4a6640ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=695376e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/</a><br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=bce54a48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw</a>[/quote]<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n[我都要攬炒][時事台]一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325723</a><br />\n攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完!! 大家快D上Twitter!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360410</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n向外國抗議中國政府散播國家恐怖主義<br />\n向外媒及各國投訴香港警察包庇黑社會合作各自無差別打人，違反通例無預警開槍，已失去合法性<br />\n港鐵作為國際地鐵聯盟之一公然妄顧市民安危強逼市民離開車廂被打<br />\n黑社會涉嫌在元朗發動恐襲襲擊，主腦直指中共政府<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">自發治安戰線:</span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf52DMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf52DMn.jpg&h=ecc7650f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港防衛隊  正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342844</a><br />\n【HKSDF】香港自衛隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352390</a><br />\n民間保衛隊初形 公民團結行公義 任何抗命運動適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351343</a><br />\n【元朗恐襲】真心，如果眾籌，成立「香港自衛隊保安公司」優先過登報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346745</a><br />\n</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">思想革命戰線:</span></div></span><br />\n平民遊戲工作室出條政治片十分值得思考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357566</a><br />\n劉細良 香港內戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QbJTdHbdGIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQbJTdHbdGIU&d=%2FPdnya